Come on, Dave, come on,
don't-don't get in my head

10:56.656 --> 10:58.092
about this.Well, I don't want to,

10:58.135 --> 11:00.268
but with Yelp comes
tremendous responsibility.

11:00.311 --> 11:02.444
I don't want
the responsibility,

11:02.487 --> 11:04.620
I just want the sticker.

11:04.664 --> 11:07.188
You have to earn the sticker.

11:07.231 --> 11:09.886
Now, it's not
that not hard.

11:09.930 --> 11:11.888
You just got to add
a little bit of sunshine.

11:11.932 --> 11:15.283
Now, I've taken the liberty of
making you a little cheat sheet.

11:15.326 --> 11:18.286
Here, "Number one,
ask them how they're doing,

11:18.329 --> 11:19.896
i.e. how their day is."

11:19.940 --> 11:23.117
Their day is terrible.
Their car's broken.

11:23.160 --> 11:24.596
Ugh.

11:24.640 --> 11:27.077
Calvin, come on,
just try it out.

11:27.121 --> 11:30.080
[sighs] All right,
I'll give it a shot,

11:30.124 --> 11:31.908
man.
