11:46.227 --> 11:47.576
Hey.

11:47.619 --> 11:50.274
Hello, again. How are you?

11:50.318 --> 11:53.190
I need to dump some used
motor oil. Where do I put it?

11:53.234 --> 11:54.626
I'll tell you
where you can put it.

11:54.670 --> 11:56.498
You can put it...[coughs]

11:58.630 --> 12:02.286
