do that for our customers.

12:02.330 --> 12:06.073
But the recycling center is just
a mile up Lincoln in Altadena.

12:06.116 --> 12:07.596
It's a lovely drive, by the way.

12:07.639 --> 12:08.989
All right, fine.

12:09.032 --> 12:10.338
[Calvin chuckles]

12:10.381 --> 12:13.558
Be sure to love us on Yelp.

12:13.602 --> 12:15.038
Man...

12:15.082 --> 12:16.213
You see that...

12:16.257 --> 12:17.562
Calvin, that showed
