Hey, hello.

12:26.354 --> 12:28.138
Welcome to Calvin's Pit Stop.

12:28.182 --> 12:31.141
How can I turn
your Monday a fun day?

12:31.185 --> 12:32.752
Nailed it.

12:39.628 --> 12:41.369
So, I wanted
to show you

12:41.412 --> 12:43.588
what I'm gonna do
with my class tomorrow.

12:43.632 --> 12:45.460
Nobody can teach the difference

12:45.503 --> 12:47.767
between major
and minor keys like

12:47.810 --> 12:50.334
Stevie Wonder. [laughs]

12:50.378 --> 12:51.683
Ooh. Whew.

12:51.727 --> 12:54.948
This is gonna blow
their little unformed minds.

12:54.991 --> 12:56.819
That's awesome.

12:56.863 --> 12:59.779
You're doing a great job.
It's just...

