13:06.655 --> 13:08.004
Yup. That's me.

13:08.048 --> 13:10.485
[laughs]Yeah.

13:10.528 --> 13:11.791
And that's great.

13:11.834 --> 13:13.923
It's just, maybe you're
a little too blunt.

13:13.967 --> 13:17.492
Just a teensy weensy bit.

13:17.535 --> 13:19.755
Okay, so let me
get this straight.

13:19.799 --> 13:22.497
I'm being
"a teensy weensy bit...

13:22.540 --> 13:23.628
too blunt"?

13:23.672 --> 13:26.022
Just try to remember
they're children.

13:26.066 --> 13:28.982
Children with parents who aren't
shy about calling the principal.

13:29.025 --> 13:30.505
But, again,

13:30.548 --> 13:33.900
you're doing great,
so great.

13:33.943 --> 13:36.641
So great, but too blunt, huh?

13:36.685 --> 13:38.513
Just an eensy, teensy,
weensy bit. [chuckles]

13:38.556 --> 13:40.515
And pretty, so pretty.

